      'FIX C вАФ ACCELERATION EVENT LOGIC: Entry threshold stays at 1.5 m/s¬≤. Hysteresis continuation added at 1.2 m/s¬≤ to prevent fragmentation. Acceptance now requires sampleCount >= 2 AND deltaKmh >= 4.0 (removed sub-second duration filter, replaced with 1s-compatible sample-count logic). Rich metadata added: deltaKmh, sampleCount, mergedCount, startSpeedBand.',
      'FIX D вАФ BRAKING EVENT LOGIC: Entry stays at 1.5 m/s¬≤. Hysteresis at 1.2 m/s¬≤. Acceptance: sampleCount >= 2 AND deltaKmh >= 3.0. Rich metadata: deltaKmh, sampleCount, highSpeedStart, intensity.',
